docs.lead_paragraph: The new health care law has made Medicare enrollment season particularly complicated this year, reports Walecia Konrad in today's Patient Money column.
docs.abstract: The Medicare system is changing rapidly, in part because of requirements imposed by the new health care law. In some areas, there will be dozens, even hundreds, of coverage options.
